high_descs: Move to the bottom right side of the large wood dresser
Open the bottom right drawer to remove the watch, then close the drawer
Carry the watch to the left side of the dresser facing the lamp
anns.task_desc: Carry a watch while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Hang a right at the window and walk to the white dresser against the wall.
Open the bottom right drawer, pick up the watch inside and close the drawer.
Turn left and walk to the white dresser on the right.
Turn on the small lamp on top of the white dresser.
anns.task_desc: Examine a watch by the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Go right to face the tall white cabinet to the left of the bed.
Open the drawer on the left that is second from the bottom and take the watch out of the drawer.
Move to the left and face the lamp on the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Pick a watch up and turn a lamp on.
